issue.title: Environment from config properties should be displayed in Zebrunner reporting without usage of env parameter from agent.yaml file
issue.body:
When I try to use agent.yaml without the env parameter, I expect the env value from _config.properties to be visible in Zebrunner reporting.

**Actual result**: However, no env value appears in the reporting.
**Expected result**: The env value from _config.properties should appear in the reporting
